We can obtain `q ‚Č† 0` from `hpqr.1.2.1`, since `(some q : ENNReal) ‚Č† 0` implies that `q ‚Č† 0` as an element of `NNReal`. 

### Formal Proof

Replace `have hq‚āÄ : q ‚Č† 0 := sorry` with:
```lean
